  <tr>
    <td colspan="2"><h2><span style="color: rgb(137, 6, 12);">A South Indian Classic</span></h2>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Savor the unforgettable taste of Dadu’s Ghee Mysore Pak, a traditional sweet from the city of Mysore. </span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Crafted with pure ghee (clarified butter), sugar, gram flour, and a hint of cardamom, this treat boasts a buttery, dense texture that’s reminiscent of a cookie. </span></p>
